  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Registry that invites patients undergoing colorectal surgery for colorectal cancer.
      Epidemiological data is collected. The Registry includes tumor tissue and blood banks for
      analyzing different genetic mutations and disease-specific biomarkers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
